<plot>Margit Springer was a small girl from East Germany. She was only one year old when she died. She was one of thousands of refugees who died under horrible circumstances in Denmark after it's liberation from the German occupation in 1945. Now, 58 years later, Margit's sister has agreed to return to Denmark to tell her and Margit's story.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?298953</url></doc>
